Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:10.28,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}Life’s just a tightrope, why not stop to fool around?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.78,0:23:10.28,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}人生就是一場走鋼絲  為何不停下享樂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.58,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}"Chaotic good" is peak right now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:12.58,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}混亂已至巔峰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:13.54,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}I can show ya how
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.58,0:23:13.54,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}我會帶你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.75,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}Don’t get confused, we are not the same
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:17.75,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}別誤會了  我們不是一路人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:19.50,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}I’m a ruthless dame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:19.50,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}我可是個悍婦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:25.47,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}"Good vs Evil" is so overdone
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:25.47,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}正義對決邪惡有點誇張了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:27.22,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}Let’s all kick back and party
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:27.22,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}讓我們一腳踹開是非開趴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:28.47,ED - EN/JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}Just leave it to moi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:28.47,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur5\3c&H3416B6&}全交給我吧
